
'''''Drexciya'''''   ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]] yasohotse 2010 akaba documentary film ntoya  yayoboye na Akosua Adoma Owusu afatanije na California Institute wa Arts (CalArts)<ref>Drexciya (2010) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › drexciya</ref>. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu ikinamico mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam 2011 kandi yitabira ''Video ya Changing Same'' mu nzu ndangamurage ya Studio i Harlem, muri New York<ref>Drexciya (2010) Movie. Where To Watch Streaming Online <nowiki>https://moviefit.me</nowiki> › titles › 166085-drexciya</ref> <ref>Drexciya - Films - Akosua Adoma Owusu <nowiki>https://akosuaadoma.com</nowiki> › artwork › 2948371-Drexciya</ref>.

== Inyandiko ==
''Drexciya''   yerekana ikigo cyo koga rusange cyatawe giherereye i Accra, muri [[Gana]] cyashyizwe kuri Riviera. Riviera icyarimwe yari iterambere ridasanzwe<ref>Ghanaian movie “Drexciya” got special mention of the jury at ... <nowiki>https://www.modernghana.com</nowiki> › entertainment › ghana...</ref>, rigizwe nizamuka ryiza cyane hamwe na hoteri yinyenyeri eshanu. Kuva mu myaka ya za 70, Riviera yaguye mubihe bidasanzwe<ref>The Future Weird: In Search Of A Black Atlantis - OkayAfrica <nowiki>https://www.okayafrica.com</nowiki> › black-film-the-future-wei...</ref>. Iyi documentaire ngufi yahumetswe n imigani ya afro-futurist yakwirakwijwe nitsinda rya Drexciya ryitwa Detroit<ref>Akosua Adoma Owusu | Pursuer <nowiki>https://africanyouthexcellence.org</nowiki> › pursuers_akosua_o...</ref>. Bavuga ko Drexciya ari umugani w’amazi utuwe n’abana bataravuka b’abagore b’abanyafrika bajugunywe mu nyanja mu gihe cy’ubucuruzi bw’abacakara ba Trans-Atlantike<ref>Short Films by Akosua Adoma Owusu - The Criterion Channel <nowiki>https://www.criterionchannel.com</nowiki> › short-films-by-akos...</ref>. Aba bana bamenyereye kandi bahinduka kugirango bahumeke mumazi<ref>Drexciya - Ghana Film Industry <nowiki>http://www.ghanafilmindustry.com</nowiki> › tag › drexciya</ref>.

